icial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e5%af%a9%e6%98%93%2c432%2c20220527%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,審易,432,20220527,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"審易","JNO":"432","JDATE":"20220527","JTITLE":"違反藥事法"}